    <item>
      <title>All This for a Cat Gif?</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/all-this-for-a-cat-gif/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Jan 2026 16:07:28 +0530</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/all-this-for-a-cat-gif/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://picsum.photos/512/256&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;Cat Gif&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    &#xA;  /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;figcaption&gt;Cat Gif&lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;button class=&#34;counter-btn&#34;&gt;Count: &lt;span class=&#34;counter-value&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;script&gt;&#xA;    (function () {&#xA;        const btn = document.currentScript.previousElementSibling;&#xA;        const value = btn.querySelector(&#34;.counter-value&#34;);&#xA;&#xA;        let count = 0;&#xA;        btn.addEventListener(&#34;click&#34;, () =&gt; {&#xA;            value.textContent = ++count;&#xA;        });&#xA;    })();&#xA;&lt;/script&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;In order to fully understand this, we must first understand a few things&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;The client-server architecture, i.e what&amp;rsquo;s a client and what&amp;rsquo;s a server?&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s JavaScript and why do we need it?&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s V8 Engine?&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;client-server-architecture&#34;&gt;Client Server Architecture&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;server&#34;&gt;Server&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You can think of it as a shopkeeper or a receptionist&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Getting started</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/zeno/getting-started/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Jan 2026 13:38:37 +0530</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/zeno/getting-started/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-why-behind-it&#34;&gt;The &amp;ldquo;Why&amp;rdquo; behind it.&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Writing an OS is hard. Incredibly so.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve learned that the hard way while trying to write this blog.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;There are a lot of things can go wrong, and not many ways to figure out what did.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;But&lt;/strong&gt;.. as humans, that is exactly what we like. Things that challenge us, that push us to our limits.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Figuring things out, learning as we encounter new things, and constantly moving forward, that&amp;rsquo;s what we are.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Leaving the Kernel dependencies behind</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/zeno/leaving-the-kernel-dependencies-behind/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Jan 2026 13:38:37 +0530</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/zeno/leaving-the-kernel-dependencies-behind/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;In the &lt;a href=&#34;../getting-started&#34;&gt;previous post&lt;/a&gt; we settled on using Rust to write our OS so we&amp;rsquo;ll set up a new rust application.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Make sure you&amp;rsquo;ve got rust installed on your computer.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s a &lt;a href=&#34;https://rust-lang.org/tools/install/&#34;&gt;guide&lt;/a&gt; on how to do that.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Now let&amp;rsquo;s create a new rust application.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve chosen to call our OS &lt;strong&gt;&amp;ldquo;Zeno&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt; (no particular reason, just sounds cool)&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;figure class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;pre&#xA;        tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&#xA;        class=&#34;chroma&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-fish&#34; data-lang=&#34;fish&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#9893a5&#34;&gt;# create a new cargo project called &amp;#39;zeno&amp;#39;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#d7827e&#34;&gt;cargo&lt;/span&gt; new zeno&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#9893a5&#34;&gt;# run our application for good luck&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#d7827e&#34;&gt;cargo&lt;/span&gt; run&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d7827e&#34;&gt;Finished&lt;/span&gt; `dev` profile &lt;span style=&#34;color:#797593&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;unoptimized + debuginfo&lt;span style=&#34;color:#797593&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; target&lt;span style=&#34;color:#797593&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#d7827e&#34;&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#797593&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; in &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ea9d34&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;.00s&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;     &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d7827e&#34;&gt;Running&lt;/span&gt; `target/debug/zeno`&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#d7827e&#34;&gt;Hello&lt;/span&gt;, world!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Great! the hardest part is done now.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
